      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. I'll look into the scrap logging and the bin check procedures. One more thing though—the warehouse manager is being pretty skeptical. He's convinced it's something more \"mysterious\" or just \"unaccounted for\" because it's so random and hard to pin down. Do you think there are any other hidden factors we're missing, or is it really just those basic human/process errors you mentioned?",
